gui.gameover.tip_prefix=Tip:
gui.gameover.tip1=Stay away from the ocean!
gui.gameover.tip2=Squids become permanently hostile in Hardmode.
gui.gameover.tip3=Squids can be killed for calamari, the best food item.
gui.gameover.tip4=Punch mobs off cliffs for an easy kill.
gui.gameover.tip5=You can sprint-punch mobs to deal additional knockback.
gui.gameover.tip6=Snowballs are great for hunting.
gui.gameover.tip7=The Bonus Chest gives you a stone sword. Sometimes that’s all you need.
gui.gameover.tip8=Mobs with iron tools have more range than you do.
gui.gameover.tip9=Creepers will explode quickly if caught on fire! Beware of chain reactions!
gui.gameover.tip10=Lit Brick Ovens will set fire to flammable blocks in front of them.
gui.gameover.tip11=Slowness will prevent you from jumping, sprinting, and climbing ladders.
gui.gameover.tip12=Mobs grow stronger as you progress. Don't underestimate them!
gui.gameover.tip13=Mountains and high points make for great shelter.
gui.gameover.tip14=Jungle Trees can be climbed for a quick and easy shelter on early nights.
gui.gameover.tip15=Mobs will not spawn for the first 90 seconds… make use of it!
gui.gameover.tip16=You can parry squid tentacles by blocking with your sword!
gui.gameover.tip17=Iron and Diamond pickaxes can give additional Iron and Gold from ore veins.
gui.gameover.tip18=Don't use tools as weapons - it uses twice the durability!
gui.gameover.tip19=Lit campfires can ignite adjacent campfires or brick ovens! Use your hunger wisely!
gui.gameover.tip20=Mad? Go yell at the developer on the NM Discord server. It's linked on the github release.
gui.gameover.tip21=Mob variants are very dangerous! Avoid fighting them unless you know what they do.
gui.gameover.tip22=Use Creeper explosions to get free dirt and stone!
gui.gameover.tip23=Fishing during a Full Moon is a great source of food.
gui.gameover.tip24=Always keep some torches with you if you get caught in the darkness!
gui.gameover.tip25=Bring lots of blocks when you go caving. It lets you block off dangerous paths.
gui.gameover.tip26=Think twice about getting iron armor! Heavy armor increases your hunger drain.
gui.gameover.tip27=Sometimes the best thing to do is to turn around and go home. Don't take unnecessary risks!
gui.gameover.tip28=Shallow water pools make for great bases! Mobs cannot spawn in the water.
gui.gameover.tip29=You can get a brick oven on the first day if you place clay down fast enough! Risky, but rewarding.
gui.gameover.tip30=Place campfires on 2 block tall pillars! It prevents them from burning the floor they are on.
gui.gameover.tip31=It's better to cave for diamonds than to strip-mine.
gui.gameover.tip32=Craft Bandages with wool and string. They can save your life!
gui.gameover.lategame1=It's important to take breaks. Come back stronger.
gui.gameover.lategame2=You got further than most. Be proud of that.
gui.gameover.lategame3=Progress is never wasted. Every death teaches you something.
gui.gameover.lategame4=You’ve come so far. You can go even further.
gui.gameover.lategame5=Don’t let one death define your journey.
gui.gameover.lategame6=Every time you die, you come back stronger.
gui.gameover.lategame7=You’ll remember what went wrong, and that’s how you’ll survive the next time.
gui.gameover.lategame8=Don't give up.
gui.gameover.lategame9=You'll be fine, just take a little break.

